title: Yosemite motion watch face
summary: Yosemite watch face with minimal design
description: Yosemite watch face is the free watch face for android wear it shows the time and motion of river flow that may make you feel relax - 12/24 hour format (change in the river watch setting menu)- Mobile companion app is coming soon.enjoy the Yosemite.Font: The Medic by Viktor Hammarberg (http://www.viktorh.com/)Motion footage from http://www.wedistill.io/
descriptionHTML:
Yosemite watch face is the free watch face for android wear
it shows the time and motion of river flow that may make you feel relax

- 12/24 hour format (change in the river watch setting menu)
- Mobile companion app is coming soon.

enjoy the Yosemite.

Font: The Medic by Viktor Hammarberg (http://www.viktorh.com/)
Motion footage from http://www.wedistill.io/
recentChanges: Add setting app on the phone, you can access the setting page by tap at the gear icon at the center of watch face preview (in android wear app)
